    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a reliable option for someone looking for a functional car at a budget-friendly price. While it runs and drives, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches and some minor fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car is sound, though the air conditioning is weak and it will likely need new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid workhorse that gets the job done but isn't a showpiece.",
